description:
As a User 
I Want a Common Style Throughout StoryHub
So That I can have  a good user experience

As a User
I want to have an AJAX New Story experience
So That I dont have to leave the Wall page

As a Wall owner
I want my walls to be private
So That I may keep my information Safe

As a Wall Owner
I want to be able to assign people to my private walls
So That they may contribute to them
Perform Annotation Select *after* list view flip is complete
As a User I want to be able to delete a project

As a User
I want a good design
So that I may enjoy the experience better
